Sarah Adegoke (ka amụrụ n'afọ 1997) bụ onye egwuregwu tenis na Naijiria
Ugbu a, ọ bụ onye egwuregwu tenis kachasị elu n'otu ụmụ nwanyị dịka Nigeria Tennis Federation si kwuo.

N'ịbụ onye a zụlitere na Ibadan, Oyo Steeti, Adegoke mụtara ịkụ tenis site n'aka nna ya, Adedapo Adegoke, onye ọ chọpụtara na ọ bụghị onye a zụrụ azụ mana ọ na-agụ isiokwu egwuregwu na magazin iji kụziere ya iwu egwuregwu ahụ
Ọ malitere ịnọchite anya Naịjirịa n'afọ 2010, ka ọ na-erule afọ 2014 ọ bụ nwanyị kachasị elu na tenis Naịjirịa

Ọ na-akọwa Serena Williams dị ka nnukwu mkpali ya na egwuregwu ahụ. Adegoke bụ onye mbụ gbara ọsọ na ngalaba ụmụ nwanyị ndị okenye na mbipụta nke 34 nke CBN Tennis Open Championship na 2012. Ọ bụkwa otu n'ime ndị Naijiria ole na ole rutere na ngwụcha nke Governor's Cup Lagos Tennis, ihe ọ rụzuru n'afọ 2014, Zarah Razafimahatratra nke Madagascar meriri ya na egwuregwu ikpeazụ. Na 2014 Ikoyi Club Masters Tennis Championship, Adegoke onye dị afọ iri na isii n'oge ahụ, kpatara iwe mgbe o meriri onye mmeri 2013 CBN Tennis Open Championship, Ronke Akingbade na otu ikpeazụ nke ụmụ nwanyị.

Na ọnwa Febụwarị 2017, o meriri Ikoyi Club Masters Tennis Championship Ka oge na-aga n'afọ ahụ, o meriri otu ụmụ nwanyị ndị okenye na 39th CBN Tennis Open Championship, merie Marylove Edwards. Ka ọ na-erule Disemba 2017, o meriri onye iro ya, Blessing Samuel, 6–3, 6–3 iji merie Rainoil Tennis Open na Lagos Country Club.
N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 2018, ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke mbụ na nke atọ n'otu na abụọ dịka Nigeria Tennis Federation si kwuo.
